modName: Sadris Used Wares expansion pack unofficial
summary:
A enlarged version of the shop: Sadri\'s Used Wares
Adds another floor, and more stuff.
descriptionHtml:
A enlarged version of the shop in windhelm\'s greyquarter: Sadri\'s Used Wares
It adds a basement, where the bedroom and containers are.
the house has several rare and valuable books.
I also made a \"model\" it\'s on a table in the bedroom; see pictures above

Send me messages for any bug you find, i will then fix those.
you can also send me messages for any mod request (only houses)

You can use this file in any way you want as long as you credit me as the original creator (except uploading it to skyrimnexus without doing anything with it.)
author: falloutforlife
